<br>
Unity of Fire<br>
Damage Shield by 35 (L1)<br>
Increase Fire Resist by 35 (L1)<br>
<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Classes: None<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Skill: Abjuration<br>
Allowable Targets: All<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Range to Target: 100 feet<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Resistance Check: Fire<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Spell Duration: Unknown<br>
Duration Formula: 8<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
Spell cast on you: You are enveloped in a unity of fire.<br>
Spell cast on someone: Soandso is enveloped in a unity of fire.<br>
Spell fades: The flames die down.<br>
<br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
